title: David Hurley - Wikipedia
snippet: General David John Hurley (born 26 August 1953) is an Australian former politician and military officer. A senior officer in the Australian Army, he served as the 27th governor-general of Australia from 2019 to 2024.

title: David Hurley - Simple English Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
snippet: David John Hurley AC DSC (born 26 August 1953) is an Australian former army officer. Hurley was the 27th Governor-General of Australia from 2019 to 2024. He was the Governor of New South Wales from 2014 to 2019.
